Paper: hep-th/9504079

Date: 1995-04-17

Title: Propagators on the two-dimensional light-cone

Comments: LATEX, 9pages

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D52 (1995) 6192-6194

Light-cone quantization procedure recently presented is applied to thetwo-dimensional light-cone theories. By introducing the two distinct nullplanes it is shown that the modification term in the two-dimensional masslesslight-cone propagators suggested about twenty years ago vanishs.